That was very creepy. As an identical twin, I can tell you it’s not uncommon for twin sisters to be pregnant at around the same time. As twins, a lot of our life events tend to happen at the same time, or closely together. However, what is uncommon is what this particular pair of twins is doing. It’s actually very gross. It’s kind of disgusting that they’re sharing the same partner, and that he’s okay with what’s going on.

These two sisters are a good example of what happens when you raise identical twins incorrectly. As a result they may even be mentally ill. If you notice, they behave as if they’re a single person. They dress a like, have the same boyfriend, and plan out their life events as if they were one person. They’re so in sync that they even finish each others sentences. This can be problematic because they can’t function as individuals.

People need to remember that even though identical twins look alike and have similar behaviors, they’re still individuals. Differences exist. That’s why parents need to raise twins as individuals and never treat them as a single entity. That was obviously the case with these twins.

Then again, this could all just be an act. It’s too over the top to be real. Maybe they’re just doing it for the attention and fame.
